      "message": "strictly speaking chunks of data here should be separated by a separator that is not allowed inside the chunks, e.g. \u0027\\n\u0027 or something. Or prefixed by length. Or something like that.\n\nOtherwise different data can result in same hash. E.g. \n\nextra \u003d [\"abc\", \"def\"]\nextra \u003d [\"abc:def\"]\n\nThough in practice it probably doesn\u0027t matter here (I hope).",
